cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the effectiveness of anonymization techniques in protecting individual privacy in transaction databases. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.DB (Databases), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
